{"tid":890143,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"親愛的 你去了哪？","createTime":"2018-11-05T05:50:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T05:56:47.000Z","uid":78683,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3a2946d8c4818bd8cb566d2ba02eea173cf5015d","tid":890143,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T05:50:24.000Z","msg":"親愛的 <br />\n<br />\n雖然 我倆相處時間不多<br />\n<br />\n但 我們已有肌膚之親<br />\n<br />\n儘管 很多人都反對我們的關係<br />\n<br />\n不過 都無阻我哋嘅愛<br />\n<br />\n我信 我哋係可以永恆 <br />\n<br />\n可惜 事與願違<br />\n<br />\n為何 你要那麼狠心 不辭而別<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仆你嗰街枝潤唇膏又唔知跌咗去邊</span></span>"},{"pid":"d4916096986f840c6ba06ac417e6d4ab7c28104b","tid":890143,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T05:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1xFwGAd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1xFwGAd.jpg&h=6af94e4f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}